     {q:"Newton’s first law describes how objects behave when ___.", options:["Forces have no effect on motion","No force acts on them","They have no mass","They are always accelerating with no cause"], answer:1},
     {q:"Higher frequency sound waves generally produce a ___ pitch.", options:["Unchanged","Lower","Silent","Higher"], answer:3},
     {q:"Why is it valuable to review photosynthesis, body systems, and physical science together?", options:["It helps connect and reinforce related science concepts learned across recent lessons","These topics are entirely unrelated to each other","Review provides no benefit in science","Each topic must always be studied in isolation"], answer:0}
